channel.title: RSbot, Recovery
channel.description:
since rsbot is no longer online, mabey we could start a topic to share old scripts or scripts still available? I'm currently developing a recovery site for rsbot users with an updated version of our own rsbot.
http://bit.ly/h6dCW9 it has an old powerbot, and an old woodcutting script, as well as a few other things like jdecmpiler, anyone else? [b]List of files[/b]
[ul][li]http://www.mediafire.com/?6lh6lb5ev7jn5tl ~ iDung (.Jar); - gravenfire23 [/li] [li]http://www.mediafire.com/?6lh6lb5ev7jn5tl ~ Aviansies (.Jar); - gravenfire23 [/li] [li]rsbot jar: http://www.mediafire.com/?ogbk7z1o0d31kes - gravenfire[/li] [li] Several scripts: http://adf.ly/SEJW - pure2ownage[/li] [li] Several RSbot versions http://adf.ly/SEJj - pure2ownage[/li][/ul]
